content.raw:
even though these header files are commented out, they were still installed by `ign_install_all_headers()` at the end of this file

so the API checker is not happy that there are missing header files caused by this branch. but if those headers shouldn't have been installed in the first place, better to break it now than later

[GUI] [Dbg] [Application.cc:395] Create main window

/data/ignition/ign-gui/src/plugins/WorldControl_TEST.cc:43: Failure
Value of: app.LoadPlugin("WorldControl")

Expected: true
/data/ignition/ign-gui/src/plugins/WorldControl_TEST.cc:51: Failure
